# 2.1-outline-generator.ms.md

<MIND_SCRIPT>
    <TARGET>text</TARGET>

    <TASK>
        Generate a structured outline with hierarchical sections.
    </TASK>

    <DATA>
        {{insert_topic_here}}
    </DATA>

    <STRUCTURE>
        - Title
        - Section 1
        - Section 1.1
        - Section 1.2
        - Section 2
        - Section 2.1
    </STRUCTURE>

    <RULES>
        - No paragraphs, only outline structure.
        - Terms must be concise.
    </RULES>

    <OUTPUT>
        Clean bullet hierarchy.
    </OUTPUT>
</MIND_SCRIPT>
